{%- comment -%}
  ── Debug helper ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  The sample data is dated 2026-06-19. To pin "now" for local testing against
  fixed data, UNCOMMENT the assign below (move it outside this comment block)
  and set an ISO timestamp WITH offset. Leave it commented for production so the
  recipe uses the real current time.

  {% assign debug_now = "2026-06-24T11:32:00-07:00" %}
{%- endcomment -%}
